<!--
  Status-bar icon for the verifier foreground notification.

  Must be a flat white silhouette on transparency: from API 21 the system
  masks the small icon to a single colour, so using @mipmap/ic_launcher here
  (as the old react-native-background-actions config did) renders as a grey
  blob. Shape is a shield + check — "payments are being watched".
-->
